위 표 같은경우 첫번쨰에 14, 15 연결  

두번째에  2,8  

세번째에 1,9  

마이너스 붙은 거는 ~번째 관측값, 안붙은 거는 그 번쨰에 해당하는 군집  

즉, 5번쨰 보면 5번 관측값과 4번째에서 묶이게 된 군집이 묶인경우

#### 다양한 방법



```R
hc2 <- hclust(dist(x)^2, method = "complete")   #최장 연결법
plot(hc2, labels = crime$city,main = "dendrogram : 최장 연결법", xlab='', sub='')

hc3 <- hclust(dist(x)^2, method = "centroid")   #중심법
plot(hc3, labels = crime$city,main = "dendrogram : 중심법", xlab='', sub='')

hc4 <- hclust(dist(x)^2, method = "ward.D")   #Ward
plot(hc4, labels = crime$city,main = "dendrogram : Ward", xlab='', sub='')

hc5 <- hclust(dist(x)^2, method = "average")   #평균법
plot(hc5, labels = crime$city,main = "dendrogram : 평균법", xlab='', sub='')

hc6 <- hclust(dist(x)^2, method = "median")   #중앙값법
plot(hc6, labels = crime$city,main = "dendrogram : 중앙값법", xlab='', sub='')
```

```R
par(mfrow=c(2,3))

                  centers = 3)
plot(crime[,c(3,4)], pch = 16, col =  data_k$cluster, 
     main = round(data_k$tot.withinss,2),
     xaxt='n', yaxt='n',
     xlab='', ylab='')
```

<img src="data:image/png;base64,"/>

같은 값 나오게 하기 위해 seed num 고정  

nstart 는 알아서 20(20썼으니까)번 돌린다음에 가장 좋은 값으로 골라줌



```R
par(mfrow=c(2,3))
set.seed(4)
data_k <-  kmeans(crime[,c(3,4)],
                  centers = 3, nstart = 20)
plot(crime[,c(3,4)], pch = 16, col =  data_k$cluster, 
     main = round(data_k$tot.withinss,2),
     xaxt='n', yaxt='n',
     xlab='', ylab='')
```

### k-means and k-medoids with outliers




```R
sam <- sam[,1:2]
sam %>% head()
```


```R
tail(sam,n=3) 
new.sam = rbind(sam,c(4,4)) # Adding new sample 
```


```R
row.names(new.sam)[51] = "New City"
tail(new.sam,n=3)
```

new sam = outlier(이상점)가 있는 것  



#### construct clusers 




```R
kmeans.fit = kmeans(sam,centers=2)
new.kmeans.fit = kmeans(new.sam,centers=2)
pam.fit = pam(sam,2)
new.pam.fit = pam(new.sam,2)
```


```R
# plots 
list.plot = list() 
list.plot[[1]] = fviz_cluster(kmeans.fit,
                              sam, 
                              main='K-means w/o outlier')+theme_bw()
list.plot[[3]] = fviz_cluster(new.kmeans.fit,
                              new.sam, 
                              main='K-means w/ outlier') +theme_bw()
list.plot[[2]] = fviz_cluster(pam.fit,sam, main='K-medoids w/o outlier')+theme_bw()
list.plot[[4]] = fviz_cluster(new.pam.fit,new.sam, main='K-medoids w/ outlier')+theme_bw()
plot_grid(plotlist = list.plot, ncol = 2)
```

결과 해석 : k-means는 outlier 떔에 결과 바뀌어버림  


#### validation of clustering: fviz_nbclust


fviz_nbclust 최적의 k를 찾기위한 함수적용  

wss와 silhouette 사용해봄



```R
wss = fviz_nbclust(sam, kmeans, method = "wss")
p1 <- wss+theme(axis.text = element_text(size = 8, color = "red"), 
                title = element_text(size = 8, color = "blue"))
```


```R
wss$data
```

y <- total within sum of squares 의미



```R
sil = fviz_nbclust(sam, kmeans, method = "silhouette")
p2 <- sil+theme(axis.text = element_text(size = 8, color = "red"), 
                title = element_text(size = 8, color = "blue"))
sil$data
```


```R
grid.arrange(p1, p2, nrow = 1)
```
